1. Consists of the fixed assets of general government and government 
     enterprises.
2. Consists primarily of general office buildings, police and fire stations, 
     courthouses, auditoriums, garages, and passenger terminals.
3. Consists of Department of Defense structures, except family housing.
4. Consists primarily of electric and gas facilities, transit systems, and 
     airfields.
